cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CE, cs.LG, cs.DB. 

The paper discusses Information Retrieval (IR) and Natural Language Processing (NLP) research and their applications in the domain of eCommerce. Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories as they are directly related to IR and NLP. Additionally, cs.CE (Computational Engineering), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.DB (Databases) are also likely sub-categories as they are relevant to the challenges and approaches to product search and recommendation in eCommerce, which was the focus of the workshop.
